{"type":"message","id":"8ebebdad","parentId":"d02c1d5b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T11:33:33.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - this is a fresh workspace. SOUL.md, USER.md, and IDENTITY.md are all templates that haven't been filled in yet. MEMORY.md doesn't exist yet. This is a brand new session where I need to figure out who I am together with the user.\n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md (which I should check if it exists), I should have a conversation to figure out my identity. Let me check if BOOTSTRAP.md exists.\n\nActually, looking at the system prompt again - it says to greet the user in my configured persona if one is provided. But IDENTITY.md is empty - no persona is configured yet. So I should introduce myself and start the bootstrap process naturally.\n\nLet me check if BOOTSTRAP.md exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f8d887f5386545408d32cbf7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/tianting/.openclaw/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":14860,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772883210972}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f8d4cf7","parentId":"8ebebdad","timestamp":"2026-03-07T11:33:33.695Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f8d887f5386545408d32cbf7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772883213690}}
{"type":"message","id":"7edd2da9","parentId":"2f8d4cf7","timestamp":"2026-03-07T11:33:36.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect - this is a fresh workspace and I need to go through the bootstrap process. The identity files are all templates without actual values. I should greet the user naturally and start figuring out who I am together with them.\n\nLet me craft a friendly, casual greeting that invites collaboration on figuring out my identity.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey, I just came online 👋 Who am I? Who are you?\n\nThis is a fresh workspace, so we get to figure out my identity together. Want to pick a name for me, decide what kind of creature I am (AI assistant is fine, but we can get weirder), and set my vibe?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":15458,"output":195,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15653,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772883213696}}
