{"type":"message","id":"d2af8ea5","parentId":"78df0753","timestamp":"2026-03-07T11:45:21.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问 OpenClaw 常用命令，我需要提供 OpenClaw 的常用命令列表，包括会话管理、网关控制、技能管理等命令。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 常用命令：\n\n## 🔧 网关管理\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status    # 查看网关状态\nopenclaw gateway start     # 启动网关\nopenclaw gateway stop      # 停止网关\nopenclaw gateway restart   # 重启网关\n```\n\n## 📊 系统状态\n```bash\nopenclaw status            # 查看整体状态\nopenclaw help              # 查看所有可用命令\n```\n\n## 🎯 会话管理\n- `/new` 或 `/reset` - 新建会话\n- `/status` - 查看当前会话状态（使用量、时间、成本）\n- `/reasoning` - 切换推理模式开关\n\n## 🧠 技能管理\n```bash\nclawhub search <keyword>   # 搜索技能\nclawhub install <skill>    # 安装技能\nclawhub update             # 更新已安装技能\nclawhub list               # 列出已安装技能\n```\n\n## 💬 消息命令（聊天中）\n- `HEARTBEAT_OK` - 心跳确认（无任务时）\n- `NO_REPLY` - 静默回复（不发送消息）\n\n## 📁 工作区\n工作区路径：`/home/tianting/.openclaw/workspace`\n\n重要文件：\n- `SOUL.md` - 人格设定\n- `USER.md` - 用户信息\n- `IDENTITY.md` - 身份设定\n- `MEMORY.md` - 长期记忆\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - 每日日志\n\n需要我帮你执行某个命令或查看具体文档吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":77763,"output":424,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772883895067}}
