{"type":"message","id":"75a7c73d","parentId":"c887911d","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:22:06.809Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that after setting up Samba sharing successfully, they can't find the shared folder when trying to open it in a code editor (like VS Code). This is a common issue because code editors don't always show network drives in their file open dialogs by default.\n\nLet me provide solutions for accessing the Samba share in code editors, particularly VS Code since it's the most common one.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是常见问题，代码编辑器（如 VS Code）默认不显示网络驱动器。有几种解决方案：\n\n## 方法一：映射网络驱动器（推荐）\n\n### Windows 映射为本地盘符：\n1. 打开文件资源管理器\n2. 右键\"此电脑\" → \"映射网络驱动器\"\n3. 选择盘符（如 `Z:`）\n4. 输入路径：`\\\\<Ubuntu-IP>\\UbuntuShare`\n5. 勾选\"登录时重新连接\"\n6. 完成后在 VS Code 中打开 `Z:\\` 即可\n\n---\n\n## 方法二：VS Code 直接打开网络路径\n\n### 在 VS Code 中：\n1. `Ctrl + K` → `Ctrl + O`（打开文件夹）\n2. 在地址栏直接输入：\n   ```\n   \\\\<Ubuntu-IP>\\UbuntuShare\n   ```\n3. 或输入映射后的盘符路径如 `Z:\\`\n\n---\n\n## 方法三：使用 VS Code Remote - SSH（最佳开发体验）\n\n如果是在飞牛 Ubuntu 虚拟机中开发，推荐直接用 Remote-SSH：\n\n1. VS Code 安装扩展：**Remote - SSH**\n2. 按 `F1` → 输入 `Remote-SSH: Connect to Host`\n3. 输入：`用户名@Ubuntu-IP`\n4. 输入密码\n5. 直接在 Ubuntu 中打开文件夹，无需挂载\n\n这样性能更好，且避免网络挂载的延迟问题。\n\n---\n\n## 方法四：创建本地符号链接\n\n如果想让网络路径出现在本地文件树中：\n\n```cmd\n# 以管理员身份打开 CMD\nmklink /D C:\\dev\\ubuntu-share \\\\<Ubuntu-IP>\\UbuntuShare\n```\n\n然后在 VS Code 中打开 `C:\\dev\\ubuntu-share`\n\n---\n\n## 注意事项\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 性能 | 网络挂载编辑大文件可能较慢，建议 Remote-SSH |\n| 文件锁定 | Samba 可能有文件锁定问题，保存时注意 |\n| 路径格式 | VS Code 中用 `\\\\` 或映射盘符，不要用 `/` |\n| 断开重连 | 映射驱动器勾选\"登录时重连\"避免重启后丢失 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐方案：**\n- 临时编辑 → 映射网络驱动器（方法一）\n- 长期开发 → VS Code Remote-SSH（方法三）\n\n你用的是 VS Code 还是其他编辑器？我可以给更具体的指引。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":79973,"output":716,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772900510821}}
{"type":"message","id":"8716c6c2","parentId":"75a7c73d","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:37:01.273Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 00:37 GMT+8] 就是用的方法一,最后发现是没有递归执行chmod导致的,问题解决了"}],"timestamp":1772901421269}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f734785","parentId":"8716c6c2","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:37:14.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈问题已解决，原因是没有递归执行 chmod。这是一个简单的确认回复，不需要工具调用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"👍 好的，问题解决了就好！\n\n确实，如果共享文件夹里有子目录或文件，需要递归设置权限：\n\n```bash\nsudo chmod -R 777 /srv/share\nsudo chown -R nobody:nogroup /srv/share\n```\n\n加上 `-R` 参数递归处理所有子文件夹和文件。\n\n后续如果遇到 Samba 相关的其他问题，随时找我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":80609,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80741,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772901421271}}
{"type":"message","id":"154b9143","parentId":"8f734785","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:38:14.504Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 00:38 GMT+8] 在vscode的终端里为何不能执行这些命令,直接ssh连到192.168.3.87中是可以执行的"}],"timestamp":1772901494500}}
{"type":"message","id":"be44308f","parentId":"154b9143","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:39:05.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about why they can't execute certain commands in VS Code's terminal, but they can execute them when directly SSH connecting to 192.168.3.87.\n\nThis is likely because:\n1. VS Code might be connected locally (not via Remote-SSH), so the terminal is running on Windows, not the Ubuntu VM\n2. If they're using Remote-SSH, there might be permission differences\n3. The VS Code terminal might be a local Windows terminal (PowerShell/CMD) instead of the remote Ubuntu shell\n\nLet me explain this clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是因为 **VS Code 的终端运行环境** 和你直接 SSH 连接的环境不同。\n\n## 原因分析\n\n| 连接方式 | 终端运行在 | 能执行的命令 |\n|----------|-----------|-------------|\n| VS Code 本地打开 | **Windows** (PowerShell/CMD) | Windows 命令 |\n| 直接 SSH 到 192.168.3.87 | **Ubuntu 虚拟机** | Linux 命令 |\n| VS Code Remote-SSH | **Ubuntu 虚拟机** | Linux 命令 |\n\n你现在的情况是：**VS Code 通过挂载的网络驱动器打开文件夹，但终端仍然是 Windows 本地终端**，所以无法执行 `chmod`、`chown` 等 Linux 命令。\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案一：使用 VS Code Remote-SSH（推荐）\n\n1. 安装扩展：**Remote - SSH**\n2. 按 `F1` → `Remote-SSH: Connect to Host`\n3. 输入：`用户名@192.168.3.87`\n4. 连接后，终端就是 Ubuntu 的 shell，可以执行所有 Linux 命令\n\n这样既能在 Ubuntu 环境中开发，又能直接执行命令，**不需要挂载共享文件夹**。\n\n---\n\n### 方案二：在 VS Code 中切换终端类型\n\n如果坚持用挂载方式，可以在 VS Code 中配置使用 WSL 或 Git Bash：\n\n1. `Ctrl + Shift + P` → `Terminal: Select Default Profile`\n2. 选择 **Git Bash** 或 **WSL**（如果有）\n3. 但注意：这仍然不是连接到 192.168.3.87，只是换了个 Windows 上的 shell\n\n---\n\n### 方案三：直接在 SSH 终端中操作\n\n保持现在的挂载方式用于编辑文件，需要执行命令时：\n- 打开 Windows 终端\n- SSH 连接：`ssh 用户名@192.168.3.87`\n- 在 SSH 会话中执行 Linux 命令\n\n---\n\n## 最佳实践\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  开发场景              │  推荐方案                      │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  在 Ubuntu 上开发       │  VS Code Remote-SSH           │\n│  在 Windows 上开发      │  挂载共享 + 本地终端           │\n│  需要频繁执行 Linux 命令 │  Remote-SSH（不要用挂载）      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**结论：** 安装 Remote-SSH 扩展，直接连到 192.168.3.87 开发，终端和编辑器都在 Ubuntu 环境中，最省心。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":80799,"output":875,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81674,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772901494503}}
{"type":"message","id":"a00e7bc4","parentId":"be44308f","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:44:01.873Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 00:44 GMT+8] Remote-SSH确实方便"}],"timestamp":1772901841868}}
{"type":"message","id":"f643d503","parentId":"a00e7bc4","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:44:14.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming that Remote-SSH is indeed convenient. This is a simple acknowledgment/agreement statement. I should respond briefly and naturally, maybe offer a few tips for getting the most out of Remote-SSH since they seem to be using it now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"是的，Remote-SSH 确实是开发利器！👍\n\n几个实用小贴士：\n\n- **多主机管理**：在 `~/.ssh/config` 中配置别名，快速切换不同服务器\n- **端口转发**：可以本地访问远程服务（如 `localhost:8080` → 远程服务器的 8080）\n- **文件同步**：配合 Settings Sync，本地和远程配置自动同步\n- **终端复用**：用 `tmux` 或 `screen`，断开重连后会话还在\n\n有其他问题随时找我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":81493,"output":228,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81721,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772901841871}}
{"type":"message","id":"381d980b","parentId":"f643d503","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:44:47.923Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 00:44 GMT+8] tianting@tianting:~/.openclaw$ clawhub install \"baidu-search\"\n✖ Rate limit exceeded\nError: Rate limit exceeded 报错了,看下为啥,是因为没开代理吗,怎么开呢"}],"timestamp":1772901887920}}
{"type":"message","id":"af76af94","parentId":"381d980b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:45:07.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户遇到了 clawhub install 命令的 rate limit 错误。这个错误通常是因为 GitHub API 的限制，而不是网络问题。让我分析一下：\n\n1. Rate limit exceeded 通常是 GitHub API 的速率限制（未认证用户每小时 60 次请求）\n2. 这不是代理问题，而是 API 调用次数超限\n3. 解决方案可以是：\n   - 等待一段时间（通常 1 小时后重置）\n   - 使用 GitHub Token 认证来增加限制\n   - 检查是否有本地缓存的技能可以离线安装\n\n让我先检查一下 clawhub 的配置和本地技能情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个错误 **不是代理问题**，而是 **GitHub API 速率限制**。\n\n## 原因\n\n`clawhub` 从 GitHub 获取技能包，GitHub 对未认证用户限制：\n- **每小时最多 60 次请求**\n- 超过后返回 `Rate limit exceeded`\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案一：设置 GitHub Token（推荐）\n\n1. 获取 GitHub Token：\n   - 访问 https://github.com/settings/tokens\n   - 生成新 token（无需特殊权限，默认即可）\n\n2. 设置环境变量：\n```bash\n# 临时设置（当前终端有效）\nexport GITHUB_TOKEN=你的token\n\n# 永久设置\necho 'export GITHUB_TOKEN=你的token' >> ~/.bashrc\nsource ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n3. 重试安装：\n```bash\nclawhub install \"baidu-search\"\n```\n\n有 Token 后限制提升到 **每小时 5000 次**。\n\n---\n\n### 方案二：等待速率限制重置\n\nGitHub 速率限制每小时重置一次，可以：\n```bash\n# 查看限制状态\ncurl -i https://api.github.com\n```\n\n看响应头中的 `X-RateLimit-Reset` 时间。\n\n---\n\n### 方案三：检查本地是否有缓存技能\n\n```bash\n# 列出已安装技能\nclawhub list\n\n# 查看技能目录\nls -la ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/\n```\n\n如果 `baidu-search` 已存在，可以直接使用。\n\n---\n\n### 方案四：手动下载技能\n\n如果急需使用：\n```bash\n# 克隆技能仓库\ngit clone https://github.com/openclaw/skill-baidu-search.git /tmp/baidu-search\n\n# 复制到技能目录\ncp -r /tmp/baidu-search ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 关于代理\n\n如果你确实在国内访问 GitHub 慢，可以配置代理：\n\n```bash\n# 临时设置代理\nexport https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:7890\nexport http_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:7890\n\n# 永久设置（添加到 ~/.bashrc）\necho 'export https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:7890' >> ~/.bashrc\necho 'export http_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:7890' >> ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n但 **Rate limit 错误和代理无关**，即使开了代理也会遇到。\n\n---\n\n先试试设置 GitHub Token，这是最彻底的解决方案。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":81737,"output":862,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772901887922}}
{"type":"message","id":"211bd25b","parentId":"af76af94","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:46:09.568Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 00:46 GMT+8] tianting@tianting:~/.openclaw$ curl -i https://api.github.com\nHTTP/2 200 \ndate: Sat, 07 Mar 2026 16:45:22 GMT\ncache-control: public, max-age=60, s-maxage=60\nvary: Accept,Accept-Encoding, Accept, X-Requested-With\nx-github-api-version-selected: 2022-11-28\naccess-control-expose-headers: ETag, Link, Location, Retry-After, X-GitHub-OTP, X-RateLimit-Limit, X-RateLimit-Remaining, X-RateLimit-Used, X-RateLimit-Resource, X-RateLimit-Reset, X-OAuth-Scopes, X-Accepted-OAuth-Scopes, X-Poll-Interval, X-GitHub-Media-Type, X-GitHub-SSO, X-GitHub-Request-Id, Deprecation, Sunset\naccess-control-allow-origin: *\nstrict-transport-security: max-age=31536000; includeSubdomains; preload\nx-frame-options: deny\nx-content-type-options: nosniff\nx-xss-protection: 0\nreferrer-policy: origin-when-cross-origin, strict-origin-when-cross-origin\ncontent-security-policy: default-src 'none'\nserver: github.com\ncontent-type: application/json; charset=utf-8\nx-github-media-type: github.v3; format=json\netag: W/\"4f825cc84e1c733059d46e76e6df9db557ae5254f9625dfe8e1b09499c449438\"\naccept-ranges: bytes\nx-ratelimit-limit: 60\nx-ratelimit-remaining: 59\nx-ratelimit-used: 1\nx-ratelimit-resource: core\nx-ratelimit-reset: 1772905534\ncontent-length: 2396\nx-github-request-id: 3A96:14CD86:DC7B66:F9B984:69AC562E"}],"timestamp":1772901969564}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c5a2e00","parentId":"211bd25b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:46:42.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user's curl output shows their GitHub API rate limit status:\n- x-ratelimit-limit: 60 (unauthenticated user limit)\n- x-ratelimit-remaining: 59 (59 requests left)\n- x-ratelimit-used: 1 (only 1 request used)\n\nSo they actually have 59 requests remaining! The rate limit error from clawhub wasn't due to hitting the 60 request/hour limit. It could be:\n1. A different rate limit (search API has separate limits)\n2. A temporary network issue\n3. The clawhub tool making multiple rapid requests\n\nLet me explain this to the user and suggest they try again, or set up a GitHub token anyway for better limits.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看你的速率限制状态：\n\n```\nx-ratelimit-limit: 60\nx-ratelimit-remaining: 59\nx-ratelimit-used: 1\n```\n\n你还有 **59 次请求剩余**，并不是真的达到了速率限制！\n\n## 可能的原因\n\n1. **clawhub 短时间内发起多次请求**（搜索、下载、验证等）\n2. **GitHub API 不同端点有不同限制**（搜索 API 限制更严格）\n3. **网络波动导致重试**\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案一：设置 GitHub Token（仍然推荐）\n\n即使现在没超限，设置 Token 也能避免以后遇到这个问题：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 获取 Token: https://github.com/settings/tokens\n# 2. 设置环境变量\nexport GITHUB_TOKEN=你的token\n\n# 3. 验证\ncurl -i -H \"Authorization: token 你的token\" https://api.github.com\n```\n\n有 Token 后限制从 60 → 5000 次/小时。\n\n---\n\n### 方案二：重试安装\n\n既然还有 59 次剩余，可以直接重试：\n\n```bash\nclawhub install \"baidu-search\"\n```\n\n如果还是失败，等几分钟再试。\n\n---\n\n### 方案三：检查技能是否已存在\n\n```bash\n# 查看技能目录\nls ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/ | grep baidu\n```\n\n如果 `baidu_search` 文件夹已存在，说明已经安装过了，可以直接使用。\n\n---\n\n### 方案四：手动安装\n\n```bash\n# 克隆技能仓库\ncd /tmp\ngit clone https://github.com/openclaw/skill-baidu-search.git\n\n# 复制到技能目录\ncp -r skill-baidu-search ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/baidu_search\n```\n\n---\n\n先试试直接重试 `clawhub install \"baidu-search\"`，如果还是报错，把完整错误信息发给我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":82916,"output":783,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83699,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772901969566}}
{"type":"message","id":"7cca6d0d","parentId":"4c5a2e00","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:49:17.505Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 00:49 GMT+8] 添加到 ~/.bashrc中确定是永远有效的吗"}],"timestamp":1772902157502}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a3383f9","parentId":"7cca6d0d","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:49:43.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是添加到 ~/.bashrc 是否永远有效。这是一个关于 Linux shell 配置的问题。\n\n~/.bashrc 在以下情况下会被加载：\n1. 每次打开新的交互式非登录 bash 终端时\n2. 但登录 shell（如 SSH 登录）可能加载的是 ~/.bash_profile 或 ~/.profile\n\n需要给用户解释清楚：\n1. ~/.bashrc 不是\"永远有效\"的\n2. 它只在 bash shell 中有效\n3. 需要 source 或重新打开终端才生效\n4. 某些情况（如非交互式 shell、其他 shell）不会加载\n\n让我给出准确的回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**不是永远有效**，有几个注意事项：\n\n## ~/.bashrc 的生效条件\n\n| 场景 | 是否加载 ~/.bashrc |\n|------|------------------|\n| 打开新终端（图形界面） | ✅ 是 |\n| SSH 登录 | ❌ 否（加载 ~/.bash_profile 或 ~/.profile） |\n| VS Code 集成终端 | ✅ 是 |\n| 非交互式 shell（脚本） | ❌ 否 |\n| 使用 zsh/fish 等其他 shell | ❌ 否 |\n\n---\n\n## 更可靠的做法\n\n### 方案一：同时添加到 ~/.bash_profile（推荐）\n\n```bash\n# 确保 ~/.bash_profile 存在并加载 ~/.bashrc\necho 'if [ -f ~/.bashrc ]; then\n    . ~/.bashrc\nfi' >> ~/.bash_profile\n\n# 然后添加到 ~/.bashrc\necho 'export GITHUB_TOKEN=你的token' >> ~/.bashrc\n\n# 立即生效\nsource ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n### 方案二：直接添加到 ~/.profile\n\n```bash\n# ~/.profile 被所有登录 shell 加载\necho 'export GITHUB_TOKEN=你的token' >> ~/.profile\n```\n\n### 方案三：添加到 ~/.bashrc 并确保 SSH 也加载\n\n```bash\n# 编辑 ~/.bash_profile\nnano ~/.bash_profile\n```\n\n添加：\n```bash\nif [ -f ~/.bashrc ]; then\n    source ~/.bashrc\nfi\n```\n\n---\n\n## 验证是否生效\n\n```bash\n# 1. 当前终端\necho $GITHUB_TOKEN\n\n# 2. 新开终端后\necho $GITHUB_TOKEN\n\n# 3. SSH 登录后\nssh tianting@localhost\necho $GITHUB_TOKEN\n```\n\n---\n\n## 更永久的方式：系统级环境变量\n\n如果想对所有用户生效：\n\n```bash\n# 编辑系统级配置\nsudo nano /etc/environment\n\n# 添加\nGITHUB_TOKEN=\"你的token\"\n\n# 重启后生效\n```\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n```\n~/.bashrc → 交互式非登录 shell（日常终端）\n~/.bash_profile → 登录 shell（SSH）\n~/.profile → 所有登录 shell（兼容性最好）\n/etc/environment → 系统级，所有用户\n```\n\n**推荐：** 添加到 `~/.bashrc` + 确保 `~/.bash_profile` 加载它，这样覆盖最全。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":83462,"output":796,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84258,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772902157504}}
{"type":"message","id":"3cbe0a4a","parentId":"9a3383f9","timestamp":"2026-03-07T17:03:46.395Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 01:03 GMT+8] 加了token还是报错tianting@tianting:~/.openclaw$ clawhub install \"baidu-search\"\n✖ Rate limit exceeded\nError: Rate limit exceeded\ntianting@tianting:~/.openclaw$"}],"timestamp":1772903026382}}
{"type":"message","id":"05593517","parentId":"3cbe0a4a","timestamp":"2026-03-07T17:04:15.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户已经设置了 GitHub Token 但仍然报 Rate limit exceeded 错误。这可能是因为：\n\n1. Token 没有正确设置或导出\n2. clawhub 没有正确读取环境变量\n3. 可能是 clawhub 本身的 bug\n4. 可能是搜索 API 有独立的速率限制（search API 限制更严格）\n\n让我先帮用户检查 Token 是否正确设置，然后尝试其他解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先确认 Token 是否正确设置：\n\n```bash\n# 检查环境变量是否存在\necho $GITHUB_TOKEN\n\n# 检查 Token 长度（应该是 40 个字符）\necho ${#GITHUB_TOKEN}\n\n# 测试 Token 是否有效\ncurl -i -H \"Authorization: token $GITHUB_TOKEN\" https://api.github.com\n```\n\n如果输出中 `x-ratelimit-limit` 显示 **5000** 说明 Token 生效了，如果还是 **60** 说明没生效。\n\n---\n\n## 如果 Token 没生效\n\n```bash\n# 重新设置（确保没有空格）\nexport GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\n\n# 验证\necho $GITHUB_TOKEN\n```\n\n---\n\n## 如果 Token 生效但还是报错\n\n可能是 `clawhub` 的问题，尝试：\n\n### 方案一：手动安装技能\n\n```bash\n# 1. 下载技能包\ncd /tmp\ngit clone https://github.com/openclaw/skill-baidu-search.git\n\n# 2. 复制到技能目录\ncp -r skill-baidu-search ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/baidu_search\n\n# 3. 验证安装\nls ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/ | grep baidu\n```\n\n### 方案二：检查 clawhub 版本\n\n```bash\n# 查看版本\nclawhub --version\n\n# 更新 clawhub\nnpm update -g clawhub\n```\n\n### 方案三：使用技能目录直接加载\n\n如果技能文件已经在正确位置，OpenClaw 应该能自动识别。检查技能目录：\n\n```bash\nls -la ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/\n```\n\n看看 `baidu_search` 文件夹是否存在。\n\n---\n\n先把 `echo $GITHUB_TOKEN` 和 `curl` 测试的结果发给我，我帮你判断问题在哪。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":84111,"output":621,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84732,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772903026390}}
